    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在指挥部中，你扮演一名间谍，努力阻止难以想象的破坏。 你必须潜行、战斗和欺骗，穿过无数的步兵、守卫和头目。 60 年代主题的滑稽体验将挑战玩家在预设的游戏时间内挫败恶毒霸主的破坏计划。 该游戏受到《合金装备》等怀旧经典的影响，将为自上而下的间谍游戏玩法带来亮点。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/f0ccfdb5a4da002ce0d6e36776ddc4cb.webp?t=1727977478\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/e68ae056c74de5af5fe2bac7e8dc1aff.poster.avif?t=1727977478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/e68ae056c74de5af5fe2bac7e8dc1aff.webm?t=1727977478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/e68ae056c74de5af5fe2bac7e8dc1aff.mp4?t=1727977478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在 20 世纪 60 年代中期，只有理事会致力于平衡世界超级大国的野心并防止全球毁灭。 然后，一位濒临死亡的顶级经纪人传递了一条神秘的信息，表明一名新球员已经登上世界舞台，可能会破坏这种不稳定的稳定。 破译了这条信息后，特工阿利斯泰尔·奈特接到了一项危险的任务：调查这条微乎其微的线索。 这是他上次任务失败后救赎自己的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/f0ccfdb5a4da002ce0d6e36776ddc4cb.webp?t=1727977478\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/db2f190be253c335f76272a95420e2fd.poster.avif?t=1727977478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/db2f190be253c335f76272a95420e2fd.webm?t=1727977478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/db2f190be253c335f76272a95420e2fd.mp4?t=1727977478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>消息中的地点原来是一座偏远岛屿，岛上有一座看似休眠的火山，而这座火山却被一个名为 SAINT 的未知组织占据。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/f0ccfdb5a4da002ce0d6e36776ddc4cb.webp?t=1727977478\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/083b23cb16e437efe45481c461a9fd01.poster.avif?t=1727977478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/083b23cb16e437efe45481c461a9fd01.webm?t=1727977478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304430/extras/083b23cb16e437efe45481c461a9fd01.mp4?t=1727977478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>奈特潜入后发现火山内部已经变成了一个配备了尖端武器和技术的巨大基地。 成群结队的警卫不断巡逻，让他的任务变得更加困难。</p>",
